# ── AI twin + agentic demo ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Without these, the chat (/api/chat) and agent planner (/api/agent) run in a
# graceful scripted-fallback mode — the UI still works, but answers are canned.
# Set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (locally in .env.local, and in Vercel → Project →
# Settings → Environment Variables) to make them live.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Model for the public chat + agent endpoints. Defaults to claude-haiku-4-5
# (fast + cheap, good for an anonymous public endpoint). Set to claude-opus-4-8
# or claude-sonnet-4-6 to upgrade — note the higher per-token cost on your bill.
# CHAT_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5
